query.description: Fire counts based on Australian States. Allowed values are - nsw or new south wales, queensland, victoria

request.description: The endpoints return information about total fire counts based on fire year for the three australian states - NSW, Queensland and Victoria.

request.description:
Route aus_fire_map returns the annual sum (count) of fires for a GPS coordinate (precision = .1 degree) in Australia for all years (limited to 2017-2020).

Route aus_fire_map/<year> returns the annual sum (count) of fires for a GPS coordinate (precision = .1 degree) in Australia for the year of interest (i.e. 2017)
The fields include: latitude, longitude, year, count.
